OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers
OL,6,Fbecoming less frequent this evening
OL,7,Fand overnight, with some clear spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping across the region though
OL,9,Fthe early hours of the morning. Winds
OL,10,Fslowly easing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMuch drier on Friday, though
OL,13,Fshowers are still possible in places.
OL,14,FVariable amounts of cloud with bright
OL,15,For sunny spells for many. Feeling cool
OL,16,Ffor the time of year.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
