OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FRather
OL,6,Fwindy with rain clearing northwards on
OL,7,FSaturday. Brighter with some showers
OL,8,Fon Sunday, then overnight rain
OL,9,Fclearing to brighter, showery weather
OL,10,Fagain on Monday. Feeling warm in the
OL,11,Fsunshine.
